headline.main: STRAIN ON NAZIS GROWS IN RUSSIA; Men Marching Knee Deep in Slush Where Mobility Is Essential to Germans NEW TARGET IS SELECTED Invaders Are Expected to Hit at Junction of 2 Reorganized Main Soviet Armies

lead_paragraph: VICHY, France, Oct 28 -- On the 128th day of the war in Russia news reached here from Berlin that the "desperate resistance of the Reds calls for maximum efforts on the part of the German armies." Superlatives are more than ever the rule in this campaign.
